Several on spin


fastdb_dev :

   * database host decatdb.lbl.gov
   * webserver URL https://c3-sn.lbl.gov/fastdb_dev

   * mongo
      - Overall admin user (MONGO_ADMIN_USER): admin

      - MONGO_DBNAME = fastdb_dev
        MONGO_ALERT_READER_USER = fastdb_dev_reader
        MONGO_ALERT_WRITER_USER = fastdb_dev_writer

   * postgres
      - database fastdb_dev
        user fastdb_dev
        readonly user fastdb_dev_ro

   ./configure \
       --with-external-url=https://c3-sn.lbl.gov/fastdb_dev/ \
       --with-dbhost=decatdb.lbl.gov \
       --with-dbdatabase=fastdb_dev \
       --with-dbuser=fastdb_dev \
       --with-db-passwd-file=/secrets/decatdb_postgres_fastdb_dev \
       --with-secret-key-file=/secrets/decatdb_fastdb_dev_flask_secret_key \
       --with-email-from=raknop@lbl.gov \
       --with-smtp-server=smtp.lbl.gov \
       --with-smtp-port=25 \
       --with-installdir=/web-data/fastdb_dev/install